OL,3,CMore than 30 Firefighters tackle early
OL,4,Cmorning blaze in Birmingham
OL,6,FMore than 30 firefighters were called
OL,7,Fout to tackle a large blaze in a
OL,8,Ffactory in Birmingham.
OL,10,FIt broke out off Roland Road in
OL,11,FLozells, just before 3.20am on Sunday,
OL,12,FApril 19. The flames were brought
OL,13,Funder control and the incident was
OL,14,Fdeclared over just after 7am.
OL,16,FSeveral fire vehicles remained at the
OL,17,Fsite, which is situated off the
OL,18,Fresidential road behind a set of
OL,19,Fgates. West Midlands Police officers
OL,20,Fwere also present.
