OL,3,CMore than 30 Firefighters tackle early
OL,4,Cmorning blaze in Birmingham
OL,6,FThe fire service said earlier: "We
OL,7,Fhave six crews in attendance at a fire
OL,8,Fon Roland Road, Lozells.
OL,10,F"As a precaution, if you live or work
OL,11,Fnearby, please keep doors and windows
OL,12,Fclosed. Avoid the area, where
OL,13,Fpossible."
OL,15,FRoland Road, which is close to
OL,16,FBirchfield Road, was sealed off during
OL,17,Fthe incident but was reopened.
